{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "chapter": 5,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 430.918,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.666,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, it came to pass that I, Nephi, did cry much unto the Lord my God,",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 5.846,
      "end": 8.354,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the anger of my brethren.",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 9.034,
      "end": 12.145,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, their anger did increase against me,",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 12.325,
      "end": 15.576,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that they did seek to take away my life.",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 16.256,
      "end": 18.717,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, they did murmur against me, saying:",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 18.897,
      "end": 21.451,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Our younger brother thinks to rule over us;",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 21.631,
      "end": 24.092,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we have had much trial because of him;",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 24.272,
      "end": 26.548,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, now let us slay him,",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 26.728,
      "end": 30.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we may not be afflicted more because of his words.",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 30.252,
      "end": 33.271,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, we will not have him to be our ruler;",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 33.451,
      "end": 36.934,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for it belongs unto us, who are the elder brethren,",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 37.114,
      "end": 38.739,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to rule over this people.",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 39.419,
      "end": 43.97,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now I do not write upon these plates all the words which they murmured against me.",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 44.15,
      "end": 47.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But it sufficeth me to say that they did seek to take away my life.",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 48.452,
      "end": 51.703,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Lord did warn me,",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 51.883,
      "end": 54.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I, Nephi, should depart from them",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 54.478,
      "end": 56.475,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and flee into the wilderness,",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 56.655,
      "end": 59.023,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all those who would go with me.",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 59.703,
      "end": 63.465,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, it came to pass that I, Nephi, did take my family,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 63.645,
      "end": 65.967,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also Zoram and his family,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 66.147,
      "end": 69.258,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Sam, mine elder brother and his family,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 69.438,
      "end": 72.271,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Jacob and Joseph, my younger brethren,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 72.451,
      "end": 74.076,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my sisters,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 74.256,
      "end": 76.624,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all those who would go with me.",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 76.804,
      "end": 79.59,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all those who would go with me were those",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 79.77,
      "end": 83.439,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who believed in the warnings and the revelations of God;",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 83.619,
      "end": 86.498,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they did hearken unto my words.",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 87.178,
      "end": 88.943,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we did take our tents",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 89.123,
      "end": 91.677,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and whatsoever things were possible for us,",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 91.857,
      "end": 95.526,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did journey in the wilderness for the space of many days.",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 95.706,
      "end": 99.003,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after we had journeyed for the space of many days",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 99.183,
      "end": 100.855,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we did pitch our tents.",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 101.535,
      "end": 105.9,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my people would that we should call the name of the place Nephi;",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 106.08,
      "end": 108.17,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, we did call it Nephi.",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 108.85,
      "end": 112.101,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all those who were with me did take upon them",
      "verse": "5:9",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 112.281,
      "end": 114.557,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to call themselves the people of Nephi.",
      "verse": "5:9",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 115.237,
      "end": 117.884,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we did observe to keep the judgments,",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 118.064,
      "end": 119.55,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the statutes,",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 119.73,
      "end": 122.098,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the commandments of the Lord",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 122.278,
      "end": 125.018,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in all things, according to the law of Moses.",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 125.698,
      "end": 127.463,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord was with us;",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 127.643,
      "end": 129.872,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did prosper exceedingly;",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 130.052,
      "end": 131.863,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for we did sow seed,",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 132.043,
      "end": 134.458,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did reap again in abundance.",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 134.638,
      "end": 139.375,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we began to raise flocks, and herds, and animals of every kind.",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 140.055,
      "end": 142.981,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, had also brought the records",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 143.161,
      "end": 145.901,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were engraven upon the plates of brass;",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 146.081,
      "end": 147.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the ball,",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 147.84,
      "end": 149.14,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or compass,",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 149.32,
      "end": 152.942,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was prepared for my father by the hand of the Lord,",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 153.122,
      "end": 155.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to that which is written.",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 155.845,
      "end": 159.189,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we began to prosper exceedingly,",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 159.369,
      "end": 161.18,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to multiply in the land.",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 161.86,
      "end": 164.461,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, did take the sword of Laban,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 164.641,
      "end": 167.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after the manner of it did make many swords,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 167.84,
      "end": 171.695,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "lest by any means the people who were now called Lamanites",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 171.875,
      "end": 174.151,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should come upon us and destroy us;",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 174.331,
      "end": 177.535,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I knew their hatred towards me and my children",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 177.715,
      "end": 180.316,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and those who were called my people.",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 180.996,
      "end": 183.736,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I did teach my people to build buildings,",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 183.916,
      "end": 188.514,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to work in all manner of wood, and of iron, and of copper,",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 188.694,
      "end": 191.248,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of brass, and of steel, and of gold,",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 191.428,
      "end": 193.75,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of silver, and of precious ores,",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 193.93,
      "end": 196.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were in great abundance.",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 196.978,
      "end": 199.625,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, did build a temple;",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 199.805,
      "end": 204.17,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I did construct it after the manner of the temple of Solomon",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 204.35,
      "end": 207.461,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it were not built of so many precious things;",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 207.641,
      "end": 210.242,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they were not to be found upon the land,",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 210.422,
      "end": 214.416,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, it could not be built like unto Solomon's temple.",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 214.596,
      "end": 219.844,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But the manner of the construction was like unto the temple of Solomon;",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 220.024,
      "end": 223.275,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the workmanship thereof was exceedingly fine.",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 223.955,
      "end": 229.063,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, did cause my people to be industrious,",
      "verse": "5:17",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 229.243,
      "end": 231.193,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to labor with their hands.",
      "verse": "5:17",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 231.873,
      "end": 235.635,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they would that I should be their king.",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 235.815,
      "end": 239.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But I, Nephi, was desirous that they should have no king;",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 239.478,
      "end": 243.75,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, I did for them according to that which was in my power.",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 244.43,
      "end": 248.238,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, the words of the Lord had been fulfilled unto my brethren,",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 248.418,
      "end": 250.508,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he spake concerning them",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 250.688,
      "end": 253.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I should be their ruler and their teacher.",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 253.84,
      "end": 257.044,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I had been their ruler and their teacher,",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 257.224,
      "end": 259.453,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the commandments of the Lord,",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 259.633,
      "end": 262.605,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until the time they sought to take away my life.",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 263.285,
      "end": 266.025,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the word of the Lord was fulfilled",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 266.205,
      "end": 268.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he spake unto me, saying that:",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 268.707,
      "end": 271.958,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Inasmuch as they will not hearken unto thy words",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 272.138,
      "end": 275.575,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be cut off from the presence of the Lord.",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 275.755,
      "end": 278.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, they were cut off from his presence.",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 279.639,
      "end": 282.89,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he had caused the cursing to come upon them,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 283.07,
      "end": 284.974,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even a sore cursing,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 285.154,
      "end": 286.826,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of their iniquity.",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 287.006,
      "end": 289.932,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, they had hardened their hearts against him,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 290.112,
      "end": 292.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they had become like unto a flint;",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 292.707,
      "end": 294.89,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, as they were white,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 295.07,
      "end": 297.624,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and exceedingly fair and delightsome,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 297.804,
      "end": 300.915,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might not be enticing unto my people",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 301.095,
      "end": 305.089,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord God did cause a skin of blackness to come upon them.",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 305.769,
      "end": 307.534,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus saith the Lord God:",
      "verse": "5:22",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 307.714,
      "end": 311.569,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will cause that they shall be loathsome unto thy people,",
      "verse": "5:22",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 311.749,
      "end": 314.582,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save they shall repent of their iniquities.",
      "verse": "5:22",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 315.262,
      "end": 317.816,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And cursed shall be the seed of him",
      "verse": "5:23",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 317.996,
      "end": 319.854,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that mixeth with their seed;",
      "verse": "5:23",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 320.034,
      "end": 323.006,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they shall be cursed even with the same cursing.",
      "verse": "5:23",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 323.186,
      "end": 325.787,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord spake it, and it was done.",
      "verse": "5:23",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 326.467,
      "end": 329.671,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And because of their cursing which was upon them",
      "verse": "5:24",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 329.851,
      "end": 332.173,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they did become an idle people,",
      "verse": "5:24",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 332.353,
      "end": 334.536,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "full of mischief and subtlety,",
      "verse": "5:24",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 334.716,
      "end": 338.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did seek in the wilderness for beasts of prey.",
      "verse": "5:24",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 338.925,
      "end": 341.015,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord God said unto me:",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 341.195,
      "end": 343.61,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "They shall be a scourge unto thy seed,",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 343.79,
      "end": 346.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to stir them up in remembrance of me;",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 346.478,
      "end": 349.218,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and inasmuch as they will not remember me,",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 349.398,
      "end": 351.256,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hearken unto my words,",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 351.436,
      "end": 354.594,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall scourge them even unto destruction.",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 355.274,
      "end": 360.568,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, did consecrate Jacob and Joseph,",
      "verse": "5:26",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 360.748,
      "end": 364.37,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should be priests and teachers over the land of my people.",
      "verse": "5:26",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 365.05,
      "end": 368.905,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we lived after the manner of happiness.",
      "verse": "5:27",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 369.585,
      "end": 373.347,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thirty years had passed away from the time we left Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "5:28",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 374.027,
      "end": 376.628,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, had kept the records",
      "verse": "5:29",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 376.808,
      "end": 380.43,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon my plates, which I had made, of my people thus far.",
      "verse": "5:29",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 381.11,
      "end": 383.989,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Lord God said unto me:",
      "verse": "5:30",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 384.169,
      "end": 385.609,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Make other plates;",
      "verse": "5:30",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 385.789,
      "end": 388.715,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thou shalt engraven many things upon them",
      "verse": "5:30",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 388.895,
      "end": 390.845,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are good in my sight,",
      "verse": "5:30",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 391.025,
      "end": 392.929,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the profit of thy people.",
      "verse": "5:30",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 393.609,
      "end": 395.234,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I, Nephi,",
      "verse": "5:31",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 395.414,
      "end": 398.386,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to be obedient to the commandments of the Lord,",
      "verse": "5:31",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 398.566,
      "end": 402.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "went and made these plates upon which I have engraven these things.",
      "verse": "5:31",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 403.24,
      "end": 406.259,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I engraved that which is pleasing unto God.",
      "verse": "5:32",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 406.439,
      "end": 409.318,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if my people are pleased with the things of God",
      "verse": "5:32",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 409.498,
      "end": 414.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they will be pleased with mine engravings which are upon these plates.",
      "verse": "5:32",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 415.147,
      "end": 419.745,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if my people desire to know the more particular part of the history of my people",
      "verse": "5:33",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 419.925,
      "end": 422.154,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they must search mine other plates.",
      "verse": "5:33",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 422.834,
      "end": 426.363,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it sufficeth me to say that forty years had passed away,",
      "verse": "5:34",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 426.543,
      "end": 430.258,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we had already had wars and contentions with our brethren.",
      "verse": "5:34",
      "lineIndex": 137
    }
  ]
}